Comment: 0,0:00:03.02,0:00:03.02,Default,Chapter,0,0,0,,Intro
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.19,0:00:06.31,Default,Narrator,80,80,80,,These kids are called Riders.{NOTE:少年たちはライダー。}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.31,0:00:09.69,Default,Narrator,80,80,80,,And they form kinship with monsters.{NOTE:モンスターと絆を結びし者たちである。}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.69,0:00:14.07,Default,Narrator,80,80,80,,One day, Avinia was suddenly kidnapped.{NOTE:ある日突然仲間のアユリアがさらわれてしまった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.07,0:00:15.78,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,Avinia!?{NOTE:アユリアが!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.78,0:00:22.12,Default,Narrator,80,80,80,,Mysterious Riders who call themselves the Ebon Riders appear one after another.{NOTE:さらに次々現れるブラックライダーズを名乗るなぞ謎のライダーたち。}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.12,0:00:26.63,Default,Narrator,80,80,80,,Defeated by Gale, Lute meets with Dede Geezer,\Nknown also as the Channeler.{NOTE:ゲイルに敗れたリュートは伝承ジイさん、デデ爺の元へ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.63,0:00:31.01,Default,Narrator,80,80,80,,There, in the snowy mountains,\Nhe obtains a Channeling Gem…{NOTE:彼から得た絆珠に新たなモンスターの技を入れ込むべく…}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.01,0:00:33.88,Default,Narrator,80,80,80,,…and learns how to combine skills with other Monsties.{NOTE:…雪山へ修業に向かった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.80,0:00:39.26,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, Debli is worrying about Avinia.{NOTE:そんな中ずっとｱﾕﾘｱのことが心配なデブリは…}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.26,0:00:41.64,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,I wonder how's Avinia doing?{NOTE:アユリア大丈夫かなぁ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.64,0:00:43.85,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,I hope they didn't do anything to her…{NOTE:ひどいことされてないかなぁ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.40,0:00:48.23,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,Like taking away her food…{NOTE:まさかご飯を取り上げられてたり…}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.23,0:00:50.61,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,Thanks for the fo{\fs35}o{\fs30}o…{\fs44}?{NOTE:いっただっきまーす…}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.36,0:00:56.45,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,H-How cruel!{NOTE:な…何てひどいことを…}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.45,0:00:58.49,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,O-Or maybe…{NOTE:そ-それとも…}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.49,0:01:00.74,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,They put her in a haunted house…{NOTE:お化け部屋に入れられてたり…}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.74,0:01:02.25,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,I'm scared!{NOTE:怖ーい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.62,0:01:05.50,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,Or maybe…!{NOTE:それとも！}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.50,0:01:07.75,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,Something like this…?{NOTE:何かこんな感じで…}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.47,0:01:18.55,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,How terrible these Ebon Riders are!{NOTE:何てひどいことをするんだブラックライダーズ～！}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.55,0:01:19.97,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,Wait for me, Avinia.{NOTE:待ってろ、アユリア。}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.97,0:01:22.06,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,I'm going to save you!{NOTE:今助けに行くぞ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.06,0:01:24.18,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,Ah… wait a second.{NOTE:あっ…おや？}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.18,0:01:26.14,Default,Debli,0,0,0,,Where's Avinia again?{NOTE:アユリアってどこにいるんだ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.35,0:01:32.03,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,Can Debli really save Avinia!?{NOTE:果たしてデブリはアユリアを助け出すことができるのか!?}
